description.p:
Subjects recorded the following information on dIBS symptoms daily throughout the duration of the study:
Number of normal stools/day;
Number of hard and lumpy stools/day;
Number of loose or watery stools/day;
Number of loose or watery stools/day with the symptom of urgency;
How bothersome is abdominal pain and discomfort? [7-point response scale: 0 (not at all) to 6 (a very great deal)];
How bothersome is bloating? [(7-point response scale: 0 (not at all) to 6 (a very great deal)].

Durable response during the three month study
Global IBS symptoms (weekly);
IBS symptom of bloating (weekly);
Abdominal pain (daily).
